Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,<Don't catch a cold!>
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,<Hachoo!>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:05.13,Location,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,560)}2 Years Ago Siberia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Look! A shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:18.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:26.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, is it true that your wish will be granted if you say it three times before the shooting star disappears?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:29.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what people believe in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:32.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom told me a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:39.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That there are other charms that can make you pretty or make you grow taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:40.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:45.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you wishing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:47.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Top secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:52.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, is it also true that every time a star falls, someone has died?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:55.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was just a fairy tale back when we were able to see the true starry sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:05.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:06.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.02,0:01:12.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:14.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:16.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:19.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.04,0:01:22.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So it has begun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:54.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:56.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:58.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:02.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:06.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That happened two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:10.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,On the night of the Tokyo Explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:13.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion became a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:18.05,Location,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,560)}2 Years Later Vladivostok
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:22.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Secondhand smoke is more poisonous than what you inhale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:29.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The smoke you inhale contains 5.3 to 43 nanograms of dimethylnitrosamine, which is a carcinogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:34.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,While secondhand smoke has 680 to 823 nanograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:37.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's eleven times more quinoline in the secondhand smoke than what you inhale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:41.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Which translates to 18,000 nanograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:45.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, telling a Russian to quit smoking is a bit pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:53.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, rationally thinking, it's best for me to quit. I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:58.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But that's quite unlikely as I'm not going to be one of those rumored contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:00.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:07.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When a star falls, it means a contractor has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do they even exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:13.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Want to see one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they kind of dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:21.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:22.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:29.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Glen Deveron 1968. Straight up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:30.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Your thirty-three year old sherry cask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:37.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that some dead stock was found in the back of this bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:46.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,April, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:57.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And you're August 7th, the man called "The Magician."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:04:00.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Some intelligence has been leaked to the Russian authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:03.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The FSB will carry out a raid in two days. {house search}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:07.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give up on the data I couldn't collect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's July?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:59.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You always hang out with Suou, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've had my eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get you out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's Nika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:10.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid and I always get into fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll treasure you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to cherish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:15.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please go out with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's confessing to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Argh, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What... What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:26.38,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:27.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Am I good enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? You really like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:43.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can we walk home together today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:09.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you do-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! I wasn't peeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you're holding a camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:35.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:40.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But you looked really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:52.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I mean Nika is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:53.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:57.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're just both in the photography club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants that delinquent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Of course, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's a cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's a bit of a hothead and is a year older, but not mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And his common sense is a tad different...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:12.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But he's super nice to kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's really a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:21.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So your world is all rosy now, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:24.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou! Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You have cleaning duty today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:38.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are several times in your life when your world changes overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:43.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't really know what love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:52.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I think Tanya has grasped its meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:08.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't once seen the true starry sky. Not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:14.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,One day thirteen years ago, gates appeared in Tokyo and Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:17.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The one in Tokyo is called Hell's Gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:20.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and the one in Brazil, Heaven's Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:25.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Near the gates there are unknown substances and phenomena beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, no one was able to go near them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,People are looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So what? This isn't a macro lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She meant your panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing tights! There's nothing to be embarrassed about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The world has changed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a great war, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:04.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This area wasn't too affected by the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but the change has started here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:23.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:24.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Bella.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:27.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A stray cat was after Petya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:30.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be on guard, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:36.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,the professor said he was busy again today, so he will be at the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I made a lot of food, so make sure to eat all of it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Bella! You know what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone confessed to Tanya today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's Nika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:50.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, that was a shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was pretty sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So, you have someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:07.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I don't! Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:15.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The true starry sky vanished when the gates appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The sky we see now is fabricated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:31.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That the stars in this sky are the lives of the contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:33.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:35.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:40.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:47.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Love, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:51.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's one emotion that's hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:56.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a reaction caused by the secretion of hormones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But people still rely on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:09.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that you're blessed to be able to dream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:18.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying people need to wake up from their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:25.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out. It's Mom's photo album.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:35.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to Japan and visit her one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:37.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:42.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's a mere human who's absolutely unnecessary to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:54.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:00.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to stay too long in that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:03.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But, Papa, he's my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:05.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My twin brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:08.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion doesn't care if you're family or his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just get hurt if you don't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:14.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! He's a part of our family!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You still buy her albums?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:19.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:21.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.34,DTB-Overlap,,0,0,0,,Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up from your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Time only moves forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:43.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Contractors don't have hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:48.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Petya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:56.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Petya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.99,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode 1   The Black Cat Doesn't Dream of Stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:15.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are several times in your life when your world changes overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Without warning or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:29.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:31.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:52.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya's acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:04.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:07.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't meet up with me this morning, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:13.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I realized it was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:18.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:21.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even plan to bear your child,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,so going out is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:26.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't confess to you for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:28.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Get your act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:30.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Lancernopt synchrotron radiation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A-A contractor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:09.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:16.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are no symptoms to indicate a person has transformed into a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:17.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:23.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The contractor's personality and behavioral patterns deteriorate remarkably and they end up causing a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after, the state agency takes the person into custody,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:30.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and they erase the memories of anyone who was in contact with the contractor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,using the ME that Papa is researching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya... don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here, Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:09.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've created quite a few secret passages in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:13.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So if either one of us was in danger, we could escape immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's time, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:17.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have remunerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:51.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:53.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:56.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my room, Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:07.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Bella?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,All activities at this laboratory will be halted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:26.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You won't stand out with my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:29.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:31.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Always carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:38.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you have it, we will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Bella knows the escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:47.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Bella?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They're not after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They've raided the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:17:59.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:00.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:02.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Get it back as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:06.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The priority order is Shion, the professor, and the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:06.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost the primary target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:13.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July, do you know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:19.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no glass in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What about the professor's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Shion? Or the FSB?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:27.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,An adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:29.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Asian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's wearing a mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,April, we're being tapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Cease all radio communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go with plan C.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I ask the questions here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:51.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the meteor core?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:54.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:55.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:58.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Then you are of no use to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:24.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no vomit or any other traces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm April from MI6.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:46.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Shion? Why is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:47.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Bella.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he? Where's Shion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:56.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:15.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a good girl, I'll give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:23.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:28.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it... I don't want to eat so many hamburgers to remunerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:36.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:39.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I'm gonna wake up with muscle ache tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:50.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a contractor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:51.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:15.70,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:15.70,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:26.21,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:26.21,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:35.77,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:35.77,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:41.95,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:41.95,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.70,0:22:47.05,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.70,0:22:47.05,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:46.68,0:22:51.81,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:22:46.68,0:22:51.81,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:22:51.58,0:23:00.46,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:22:51.58,0:23:00.46,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:00.28,0:23:05.55,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:23:00.28,0:23:05.55,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.29,0:23:12.50,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.29,0:23:12.50,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 6,0:23:12.13,0:23:20.09,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:23:12.13,0:23:20.09,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 7,0:23:20.01,0:23:30.38,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:23:20.01,0:23:30.38,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:42.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,BK201...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:02.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A star falls from the fabricated sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:06.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A life disappears after an ephemeral glitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:09.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The red flames erase the bonds that have formed,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:12.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and burns everything to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.61,0:24:15.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A cold blade pierces the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.22,0:24:19.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and the girl roams through the freezing city.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.49,0:24:22.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A fallen star never regains its radiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.13,0:24:24.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It only fades further.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.37,0:24:29.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And then... Another star falls.